import {ADD_PRESON} from '../constant'
const initpreson =[{id:'001',name:'ReactReducer',age:'10'}]
export default function presonReducer(preState=initpreson,action){
    const {type,data} =action
    switch (type) {
        case ADD_PRESON:
            return [data,...preState]
            
    
        default:
            return preState
    }
}
